{"id":"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale","title":"Format data based on locale","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\" translation-result=\"on\">根據語言環境格式化資料<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Format data based on locale<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 提供了以下內建的資料轉換<a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">管道</a>。資料轉換管道會使用 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 令牌來根據每個語言環境的規則來格式化資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular provides the following built-in data transformation <a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">pipes</a>.\nThe data transformation pipes use the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token to format data based on rules of each locale.</p>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">資料轉換管道</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Data transformation pipe</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">詳情</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Details</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" title=\"DatePipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DatePipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">格式化日期值。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a date value.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" title=\"CurrencyPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>CurrencyPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">將數字轉換為貨幣字串。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a currency string.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\" title=\"DecimalPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">將數字轉換為十進位制數字字串。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a decimal number string.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" title=\"PercentPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>PercentPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">將數字轉換為百分比字串。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a percentage string.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\" translation-result=\"on\">使用 DatePipe 顯示當前日期<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Use DatePipe to display the current date<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要以當前語言環境的格式顯示當前日期，請對 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 使用以下格式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To display the current date in the format for the current locale, use the following format for the <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code>.</p>\n\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ today | <a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">date</a> }}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\" translation-result=\"on\">改寫 CurrencyPipe 的當前語言環境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Override current locale for CurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">將 <code>locale</code> 引數新增到此管道以覆蓋 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 令牌的當前值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Add the <code>locale</code> parameter to the pipe to override the current value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> token.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要強制貨幣使用美式英語（<code>en-US</code>），請以如下格式使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To force the currency to use American English (<code>en-US</code>), use the following format for the <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code></p>\n\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ amount | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> : 'en-US' }}\n\n</code-example>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>注意</strong>：<br>\n為 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> 指定的語音環境設定會覆蓋應用程式的全域 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 令牌。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>NOTE</strong>: <br>\nThe locale specified for the <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> overrides the global <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> token of your application.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare component for translation | Angular\">準備翻譯範本</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare component for translation | Angular\">Prepare component for translation</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/registerLocaleData\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/glossary#pipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#下一步呢\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#使用-datepipe-顯示當前日期\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#改寫-currencypipe-的當前語言環境\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#根據語言環境格式化資料\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}